<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE reference PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DITA Reference//EN" "reference.dtd">
<reference id="api_onclientrolechanged">
    <title><ph keyref="onClientRoleChanged"/></title>
    <shortdesc>直播场景下用户角色已切换回调。</shortdesc>
    <refbody>
        <section id="prototype">
            <title>原型</title>
            <p conref="../conref/conref_rtc_api.dita#apidef/onClientRoleChanged"> </p>
        </section>
        <section id="detailed_desc">
            <title>详细描述</title>
            <p>用户角色切换后会触发该回调，如从观众切换为主播，反之亦然。</p>
            <p>该回调是由本地用户在加入频道后调用 <xref keyref="setClientRole1"/> 改变用户角色触发的。</p>
        </section>
    <section id="parameters">
        <title>参数</title>
        <parml>
            <plentry>
                <pt>oldRole</pt>
                <pd>切换前的角色: <xref keyref="CLIENT_ROLE_TYPE"/>。</pd>
            </plentry>
            <plentry>
                <pt>newRole</pt>
                <pd>切换后的角色: <xref keyref="CLIENT_ROLE_TYPE"/>。</pd>
            </plentry>
        </parml>
    </section>
    </refbody>
</reference>
